Market Dynamics
The allulose market is influenced by several key dynamics:
•	Increasing Health Awareness: Consumers are becoming more health-conscious, leading to a rise in demand for low-calorie and natural food products. Allulose fits well into this trend due to its low-calorie content and natural origin.
•	Rise in Chronic Diseases: The increasing prevalence of obesity and diabetes worldwide has prompted consumers to seek alternatives to traditional sugars, further boosting the demand for allulose.
•	Technological Advancements: Advances in production technology have made it possible to produce allulose more efficiently and cost-effectively, increasing its availability and reducing its price.
